# 📊 Sales Analytics Dashboard

## 📌 Overview
This project analyzes sales data using SQL and Power BI to generate business insights.

## 🛠 Tools Used
- SQL
- Power BI
- Excel

## 📈 Dashboard Features
- Total Sales KPI
- Total Profit KPI
- Customer Count
- Monthly Sales Trend
- Profit by Category
- Top Customers
- Top Revenue Months

## 🔍 Key Insights
- Sales show seasonal patterns across months
- Technology category generates highest profit
- A few customers contribute majority of revenue

## 📂 Files
- Sales_Analytics_Dashboard.pbix
- Orders.csv

## 🚀 How to Use
1. Download `.pbix` file
2. Open in Power BI Desktop
3. Explore dashboard

